# CLI Trivia Night

A command-line trivia game built in JavaScript using Node.js. Answer fun and quirky questions under a 15-second timer â€” can you beat the clock and get a perfect score?

---

##  Features

- Interactive command-line interface
- 15-second countdown timer per question
- Humor-based questions and answers
- Final score breakdown with correctness for each question
- Play again menu
- Start menu with Yes / No / Maybe logic

---

##  How to Run

1. **Clone the repo:**
   ```bash
   git clone 
   run npm install
   node index.js to play
